The paper is also likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it involves the use of generative adversarial networks and metric learning, which are both machine learning techniques. 

The multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper deals with image synthesis.
